            <h2 class="panel-title">Environmental conservation funding for Indigenous Peoples</h2>
        </header>

        <div class="panel-body">
            <div class="mwsbodytext text parbase section">
    

    
        <p>Find federal programs that help fund environmental initiatives with Indigenous leadership.</p>
<p><a class="btn btn-lg btn-default btn-block" href="https://www.canada.ca/en/environment-climate-change/services/climate-change/indigenous-partnership/funding.html" role="button">Find funding programs</a></p>

    


